-- Greek debt restructuring not in the cards: EU exec
-- 
-- Mon May 16, 2011 8:12am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/05/16/us-eu-greece-restructuring-idUSTRE74F1YU20110516

 

 BRUSSELS  (Reuters) - Greek debt restructuring is not being considered, European Commission spokesman Amadeu Altafaj said on Monday. 

 "Debt restructuring is not in the cards for Greece," Altafaj told a regular news briefing. (Reporting by  Jan Strupczewski , editing by Rex Merrifield)